		<title>狗狗的愛不用說！這「5個」小動作代表牠在默默守護主人</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/08/23/%e7%8b%97%e7%8b%97%e7%9a%84%e6%84%9b%e4%b8%8d%e7%94%a8%e8%aa%aa%ef%bc%81%e9%80%99%e3%80%8c5%e5%80%8b%e3%80%8d%e5%b0%8f%e5%8b%95%e4%bd%9c%e4%bb%a3%e8%a1%a8%e7%89%a0%e5%9c%a8%e9%bb%98%e9%bb%98%e5%ae%88/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報 時事新聞]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Sat, 23 Aug 2025 07:24:13 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[新寵]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[時事]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[主人]]></category>
