		<title>狗狗這些習慣正常嗎？小心這「7種」行為透露健康警訊 !</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/08/23/%e7%8b%97%e7%8b%97%e9%80%99%e4%ba%9b%e7%bf%92%e6%85%a3%e6%ad%a3%e5%b8%b8%e5%97%8e%ef%bc%9f%e5%b0%8f%e5%bf%83%e9%80%99%e3%80%8c7%e7%a8%ae%e3%80%8d%e8%a1%8c%e7%82%ba%e9%80%8f%e9%9c%b2%e5%81%a5%e5%ba%b7/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報 時事新聞]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Sat, 23 Aug 2025 06:01:32 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[新寵]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[時事]]></category>
